        <h3 style="margin-top:20px;">Outlook</h3>
        <p>
          If Brown continues leading Boston to one of the best records in the league while maintaining
          his two-way impact, he will remain firmly in the MVP conversation. His ability to elevate his
          play in big moments makes him a serious contender.
